子很匪夷所思怎麽可以30~40元買到iphone。但是一旦接觸過的，肯定不會再去~所以這一類網站基本上就出現很短時間，圈了一筆錢就消失了，澳洲當時就查封了很多這樣的網站。<br />\n<br />\n這種騙局終于去到HK，希望HK儘早立法，拉得。<br />\n希望大家廣傳，咪上當~"},{"pid":"e2041f34ea63ef2dc4c2ce5a37501daad3a34059","tid":283457,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"usa都冚哂啦"},{"pid":"15474abc8a624f38ed6180c3e7fb9fa1ef24b840","tid":283457,"uid":60258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"咁csgo d 賭槍網算唔算犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9064e9acfef7437fe83f4db0f36808d25d689737","tid":283457,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:30:40.000Z","msg":"留名睇佢收皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8082a86d97b89659616ae58ed0c8d52b9ba35e","tid":283457,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:32:25.000Z","msg":"報驚啦"},{"pid":"628e19f23a9929b7996f4360500ae1fc7ce7140a","tid":283457,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁csgo d 賭槍網算唔算犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGoogle YouTuber Tmartin<br />\n起個賭槍網自己又做球員又做球證，跟住畀人告，連Steam都ban哂所有賭槍網"},{"pid":"56f142ee6107ba3508b2b93623d21edfeeabfe37","tid":283457,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>app照開<br />\n香港禁左佢（因為賭博成分）<br />\n<br />\n如果市民用vpn黎玩嘅就即係玩外圍<br />\n拉晒佢地<br />\n再拉埋個莊</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e7b781fc19cee6919970a753690969f09b837dfd","tid":283457,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T11:50:04.000Z","msg":"Report完應該好快bam"},{"pid":"14d431a0b25b2c765a91bad7e3f864d9fac3722a","tid":283457,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkg