e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:35:11.000Z","msg":"就算唔出術，呢種拍賣個莊都唔會輸<br />\n純粹呃傻仔"},{"pid":"68a23333fc524ead178d7df18d883761deb6dfa6","tid":283457,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點會覺得冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落左bid無論你bid唔bid得到你都收唔返個credit<br />\n定係我理解錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢叫你用佢訂個價去買件貨，買完就還翻d credit畀你<br />\n咁佢就賺左來貨同賣出既差價<br />\n如果你唔買，佢就賺credit錢<br />\n所以冇得輸果個係周柏豪</blockquote><br />\n一定唔到我地 bid 到啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最賤唔限時間stop個bid ,咁寫個bot 9秒自動出價，呢世都唔會有人bid到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965329de86527b66c539522fae03b3cea1b5918d","tid":283457,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b1949c4693905b696453f7eeb76f1405cadb13","tid":283457,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"仲以為你講緊唱櫻花樹下嗰個周柏豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}